{"tid":2143190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不明物資運入中山紀念公園體育館 大批黨衛軍駐守 曾引用599G警告","createTime":"2020-08-07T03:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T03:09:20.000Z","uid":21470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb951728d4c7800fc9c1580defe50ae117d9276","tid":2143190,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:05:32.000Z","msg":"區議員促解釋物資運入中山紀念公園體育館用途<br />\n最後更新時間 2020-08-07 10:35<br />\n<br />\n一輛車身掛上「華大基因火眼實驗室援港物資」橫額的貨車，昨晚將一批物資運送到中山紀念公園體育館。在中山紀公園體育館外，早上起有大批警員戒備，不時有警員進出場館。<br />\n<br />\n多名中西區區議員到場視察，中西區區議會主席鄭麗瓊指，不清楚相關物資運入場館的用途，區議會亦沒收過任何通知，昨晚起收到多名居民查詢，因此約同多名議員到場召開特別會議。警方以違反禁止群眾聚集規例為由，多次向在場區議員發出警告，要求盡快離開。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351070\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2351070&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLMtNvD6oN5AbUd1%2F%2Bp%2BoAYU%3D&h=0105bc1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2351070</a>"},{"pid":"2fb6a8cfda65cbc5353a1c9c9f1070a3bc734e1e","tid":2143190,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265f56243acdb88d46c70f348a168a16cca7edba","tid":2143190,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T03:09:20.000Z","msg":"根本就係方便住西環班中聯辦"}]}